      "post_content": "This card is amazing. Really shines in a mono deck, when you rarely would get color screwed. Does not come into play tapped, and will tap for ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol). Ramps when you need it to, this is a 5/5 land for me. Balanced and powerful.",
      "posted_by": "TheWrathofShane",
